{"id":467,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/467","type":2,"name":"ぼくらの","name_cn":"地球防卫少年","summary":"       暑假，来到自然学校的15名少年少女。在那里，他们遇到了一个自称为“KOKOPERI”（可可贝利）的神秘大叔，邀请和他们开始一场“游戏”。所谓的“游戏”就是操纵巨大机器人来对抗袭击地球的机器人，以为这是一般电脑游戏的15名孩子们定下了契约，但孩子们不知道这个游戏的真正意义，更不知道操纵机器人背后的沉重代价。在一次又一次的战斗中， 孩子们从不知到真相而对这个游戏的激动兴奋，到知道真相后看着同伴慢慢离开的痛苦，看着每次选择驾驶者也许就是自己却无法解除契约时各自的不同表现，展现了人性中最真实的一面——恐慌、愤怒和悲伤，并通过每个孩子独一无二的人生经历暴露出世界的黑暗一面。","eps":[{"id":289,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/289","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"ゲーム","name_cn":"Game","duration":"25m","airdate":"2007-04-09","comment":9,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":290,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/290","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"ジアース","name_cn":"Zearth","duration":"25m","airdate":"2007-04-16","comment":18,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":291,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/291","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"秘密","name_cn":"Secret","duration":"25m","airdate":"2007-04-23","comment":7,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":292,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/292","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"強さ","name_cn":"Strength","duration":"25m","airdate":"2007-04-30","comment":10,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":293,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/293","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"弱さ","name_cn":"Weakness","duration":"25m","airdate":"2007-05-07","comment":6,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":294,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/294","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"情欲","name_cn":"Lust","duration":"25m","airdate":"2007-05-07","comment":7,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":295,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/295","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"傷","name_cn":"Wound","duration":"25m","airdate":"2007-05-21","comment":13,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":296,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/296","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"復讐","name_cn":"Revision","duration":"25m","airdate":"2007-05-28","comment":16,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":297,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/297","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"家族","name_cn":"Family","duration":"25m","airdate":"2007-06-05","comment":10,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":298,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/298","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"仲間","name_cn":"Companion","duratio